quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  33,51,"Olindiriza oyo gwoba oyagadde ku bo ate nootwala oyo gwoba oyagadde ate oyo gwoba osazeewo mu abo boolindirizza tolina kibi (singa oba osazeewo noomutwala) ekyo kye kitandikirwako mu kutebenkeza amaaso gaabwe ne batanakuwala era bonna nebasiima ebyo byoba obawadde, era Katonda amanyi ebyo ebiri mu mitima gya mmwe, anti bilijjo Katonda mumanyi nnyo wa kisa"
  33,52,"Tokkirizibwa bakyala balala oluvanyuma lw'abo (boolina) wadde okubawaanyisaamu abakyala abalala, obulungi bwabwe ne bwe bukusanyusa butya okugyako abo omukono gwo ogwa ddyo begufuga, era bulijjo Katonda mulondoozi wa buli kintu"
  33,53,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza temuyingiranga e nyumba za Nabbi okugyako nga mukkiriziddwa okugenda okulya (ate) nga temulinda kuyiisibwa kwa mmere, bwe mumala okulya olwo nno musaasaane era temutwalirizibwanga emboozi, mazima ekyo kibadde kinyiiza Nabbi ate nga abakwatirwa ensonyi so nga Katonda takwatibwa nsonyi kwogera mazima, era (bakyala ba Nabbi) bwe mubaako ekintu kye mubasaba mukibasabire mabega wa lutimbe, ekyo nno kyekisinga obutukuvu eri emitima gya mmwe n'emitima gyabwe. Tekibagwanira mmwe okunyiiza omubaka wa Katonda era tekibagwanira kuwasa bakyalabe oluvanyumalwe (nga ekiragiro kino) kya lubeerera. Mazima ekikolwa ekyo kinene ewa Katonda"
  33,54,Kamube nga mwolesezza ekintu oba nga mukikwese mazima Katonda bulijjo amanyidde ddala ekifa ku buli kintu
  33,55,"(Bakyala ba Nabbi) tebalina kibi (obuteebikka) nga bali ne ba kitaabwe, wadde abaana baabwe wadde bannyinaabwe, wadde abaana ba bannyinaabwe, wadde abakyala nga bbo, wadde emikono gyabwe egya ddyo begifuga, bateekeddwa okutya Katonda, mazima Katonda bulijjo aba buli kintu kyonna wekikolerwa"
  33,56,"Mazima Katonda neba Malayikabe basaasira Nabbi, abange mmwe abakkiriza mumusabirenga era mumulamuse olulamusa (olumuwa ekitiibwa)"
  33,57,"Mazima abo abanyiiza Katonda n’omubakawe, Katonda yabakolimira ku nsi ne ku nkomerero era naabategekera ebibonerezo ebinyoomesa"
  33,58,"Ate abo abanyiiza abakkiriza abasajja n’abakkiriza abakazi awatali kintu kye bakoze, mazima baba beetisse okutemerera n'ekibi eky'olwatu"
  33,59,"Owange ggwe Nabbi gamba bakyalabo ne bawalabo ne bakyala ba bakkiriza babe nga beebikkirira obukaaya bwabwe, ekyo kye kyanguya okuba nga bamanyika (nti ba kitiibwa) olwo nno baleme kunyiizibwa. Bulijjo Katonda muyitirivu wa kusonyiwa era muyitirivu wa kusaasira"